273
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:35,330
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

274
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:38,056
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

275
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:41,220
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

276
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:45,010
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

277
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:51,540
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

278
00:14:52,190 --> 00:14:55,506
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

279
00:14:55,530 --> 00:14:59,060
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

280
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:05,810
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

281
